<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link><atom:link href="http://rsshub.app/weibo/user/2831150640" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description>深圳卫健委的微博 - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><generator>RSSHub</generator><webMaster>i@diygod.me (DIYgod)</webMaster><language>en</language><image><url>https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.600.600.180/a8bfee30ly8hp22ftggynj20go0gomyy.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1714691649&amp;ssig=kNxyTIgni0</url><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:14:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><ttl>1</ttl><item><title>🥒丝瓜发苦还能吃吗？丝瓜、黄瓜、葫芦等会发苦，是因为在在特殊条件下产生了一种有毒物质——葫芦素。即使经过加热，葫芦素也很难被破坏，食用后可能会引起食...</title><description>🥒丝瓜发苦还能吃吗？&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;丝瓜、黄瓜、葫芦等会发苦，是因为在在特殊条件下产生了一种有毒物质——葫芦素。即使经过加热，葫芦素也很难被破坏，食用后可能会引起食物中毒，轻则头晕、腹泻、恶心等，重则腹痛、休克，甚至导致死亡。因此，这类食物味道发苦，就不要再吃了。&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[并不简单]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫来辟谣#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（科普中国）&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;建议直接吃苦瓜&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[doge]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hpbblck0k0g20hs09lair.gif&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/Ocr8K214s</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/Ocr8K214s</guid><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:55:19 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>【[举杠铃]无氧运动过量可能诱发急性痛风？】真的有可能[裂开]！有些无氧运动运动量过大，会造成体内乳酸堆积、尿酸排泄出现障碍。其次，大量运动后出汗多、尿量...</title><description>【&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[举杠铃]&quot; src=&quot;https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/bb/2022_Weightlifting_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;无氧运动过量可能诱发急性痛风？】真的有可能&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[裂开]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;！有些无氧运动运动量过大，会造成体内乳酸堆积、尿酸排泄出现障碍。其次，大量运动后出汗多、尿量减少，若不及时补水，血尿酸可能骤升，诱发急性痛风关节炎。&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[话筒]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;医生建议：运动要适度，注意量力而行；即使不渴也要注意多喝水，维持代谢平衡。&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8